[SHORT DESC]
Cures poison.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>The Antidote heals the status of poison or toxic poison from one Pokemon when used by the trainer. If a Pokemon holds Antidote as an item, it will not activate even if the holder is poisoned. It costs four points per use in the Wonder Launcher.</p>

<h2>Location</h2>
<p>All PokeMarts after obtaining one badge, 100 Pokemon Dollars.</p>